171
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:40,500
I can't help you.
我帮不上你的忙

172
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,330
Well, fine.
喔，好吧

173
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:45,440
If I'm the only person with any appreciation...
如果我是唯一愿意欣赏…

174
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:49,470
of the sanctity of the written word, then I'll go defend it myself.
书写文字之美的人 我会亲自去捍卫它

175
00:10:50,110 --> 00:10:52,100
Don't you follow me.
别跟着我

176
00:10:56,950 --> 00:10:59,940
-How did it go with Erin? -Unbelievable.
-你跟艾玲玩得还开心吗？ -真是不可思议

177
00:11:00,190 --> 00:11:02,160
We had the best time.
我们玩得非常开心

178
00:11:03,290 --> 00:11:06,950
-So you're not mad anymore? -No, no. You guys were totally right.
-你不再生我们的气了？ -不，你们是对的

179
00:11:07,130 --> 00:11:09,360
This was much better than the first date.
这次比我们第一次约会棒得多

180
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:12,120
It was awkward. We were both nervous.
那真的很尴尬，我们都很紧张

181
00:11:12,370 --> 00:11:15,430
-Didn't you sleep together? -Yeah, that calms me down.
-你们不是上过床了？ -对，那让我冷静下来

182
00:11:17,570 --> 00:11:19,440
And we have so much in common.
我们有很多共通点

183
00:11:19,670 --> 00:11:24,810
She loves sandwiches, sports. Although she is a Met fan.
她喜欢三明治，运动 虽然她是大都会队的球迷

184
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:27,980
Not an issue now, but if we had kids...
现在那不是问题 但如果我们有了孩子…

185
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:32,120
Oh, my God! Listen to you talking about having kids.
我的天啊！你竟然会提到生孩子的事

186
00:11:32,890 --> 00:11:35,650
Oh, my Joey.
喔，我的乔伊

187
00:11:35,890 --> 00:11:38,150
Please don't get married before I do.
求求你别比我先结婚

188
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:48,130
I just cannot believe that Clark stood me up.
我不敢相信克拉克会放我鸽子

189
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,830
He may still show up.
他应该会来

190
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:51,300
What are you, stupid?
你是笨蛋吗？

191
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:56,100
-It's been three hours. -Is that all?
-我们已经等了三小时 -只有三小时吗？

192
00:11:57,040 --> 00:12:00,670
Let's go on to happier things.
谈一些比较快乐的事

193
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:03,410
Why don't you tell me about your lovely wedding.
你为什么不告诉我你们的婚礼呢？

194
00:12:03,650 --> 00:12:08,420
There was something that we wanted to tell you about the wedding.
关于我们的婚礼 有件事我们想告诉你

195
00:12:08,690 --> 00:12:11,920
It's going to be a small ceremony.
婚礼的规模很小

196
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:13,820
Tiny.
小到不行

197
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:17,760
We're not even sure why we're having it.
我们甚至不知道为什么要举行婚礼

198
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:21,660
It's actually going to be just family.
事实上我们只会邀请家人来参加

199
00:12:22,870 --> 00:12:26,330
Oh, wait.
喔，等一下

200
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:30,200
You two think of me as family?
你们把我当家人看待？

201
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:37,180
I have to ask you something now, and be honest.
我得问你们一件事，请老实地回答我

202
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:42,010
Do you want me to sing "Careless Whisper" or "Lady in Red"?
你们要我唱《无心呢喃》 或《红衣女郎》？

203
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:47,660
How can you say that? The Mets have no closer.
你怎么能那么说？ 大都会队也好不到哪里去

204
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:51,160
-What about Benitez? -What about game one of the series?
-班尼提兹呢？ -第一场比赛呢？

205
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:53,870
-What about shut up? -You shut up.
-你为什么不闭嘴？ -你才要闭嘴

206
00:12:54,700 --> 00:12:56,800
I love arguing with her.
我喜欢跟她吵架

207
00:12:57,070 --> 00:12:58,870
-Be right back. -Okay.
-我马上回来 -好的

208
00:13:00,610 --> 00:13:01,910
How's it going with Joey?
你跟乔伊进行得如何？

209
00:13:02,110 --> 00:13:04,080
Oh,okay.
还好

210
00:13:04,310 --> 00:13:05,710
Okay?
还好？

211
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:09,910
Tell me that you like him, please. I mean, tell me that you like him.
请告诉我你喜欢他 告诉我你真的喜欢他

212
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:14,480
He's a really great guy,and I know you really want this to work out...
他真的很棒，我知道 你们希望我们能成功…

213
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:17,690
but I just don't see this having a future.
但我不觉得我们会有未来

214
00:13:20,230 --> 00:13:23,090
But you said that you liked him. What happened?
但你说过你喜欢他，发生了什么事？

215
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:26,090
Did you just change your mind?
你改变了心意吗？

216
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:29,300
-Kind of. -Then change it back!
-可以那么说 -那么快改回来

217
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:34,130
I'm sorry. It's just, there's no real spark.
对不起，我们之间真的没有火花

218
00:13:34,340 --> 00:13:36,210
Didn't you sleep together?
你们不是上过床了吗？

219
00:13:36,610 --> 00:13:37,800
Yeah.
对

220
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,740
Tramp.
荡妇

221
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:43,110
Does Joey have any idea?
乔伊知道吗？

222
00:13:43,350 --> 00:13:45,720
I don't think he does. You know what?
我想他不知道，你知道吗？

223
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:48,720
Maybe you could tell him I'm not interested...
或许你可以告诉他我不想…

224
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,860
in a serious relationship.
认真地跟别人交往

225
00:13:52,230 --> 00:13:54,520
You mean, like, that you're kind of a loner?
你是说你是个独行侠？

226
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:56,160
Yeah, that'd be great.
对，那个说法不错

227
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:59,130
And maybe that you're a real stronzo.
或许你真的是个淫娃 

228
00:13:59,300 --> 00:14:00,290
I'm sorry.
你说什么？

229
00:14:00,470 --> 00:14:04,130
I guess Italian isn't one of the four languages you speak.
我猜你会说的四种语言 不包括意大利文

230
00:14:06,510 --> 00:14:09,140
-Hey. Want to go? -Yeah, let's go.
-嘿，要走了吗？ -我们走吧

231
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:12,470
-Okay. See you guys later. -Bye,guys.
-待会见 -再见

232
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:15,540
Hey, thank you so much.
谢谢你们

233
00:14:19,150 --> 00:14:20,280
Wow.
哇

234
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:23,320
I guess it wasn't cupid that brought her here.
我猜不是丘比特把她带来这里的

235
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:27,120
No, just a regular old flying dwarf.
不，只是一个会飞的老矮人

236
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:36,700
Yes, yes. How can I help you?
怎么了？需要我帮忙吗？

237
00:14:36,970 --> 00:14:38,770
We were just looking around.
我们只是四处看看

238
00:14:38,970 --> 00:14:41,270
Oh, you're fellow scholars.
原来你们是爱念书的学生

239
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:43,980
What exactly were you looking for?
你们到底在找什么？

240
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:48,340
Perhaps Dr. Chester Stock's musings...
或许你们想看查斯特史塔克博士…

241
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:51,040
on the Smilodon californicus?
对剑齿虎的研究？

242
00:14:54,050 --> 00:14:55,180
Get out of here!
快滚！

243
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,390
Meeting someone?
你来找人吗？

244
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:09,330
Or are you just here to brush up...
还是你想来看看…

245
00:15:09,570 --> 00:15:12,510
on Merriam's views on evolution?
犸莉安对进化论的看法？

246
00:15:12,810 --> 00:15:17,370
Actually,I find Merriam's views far too progressionist.
事实上，我觉得犸莉安 的观点太先进了

247
00:15:22,020 --> 00:15:25,320
I find Merriam's views far too progressionist.
我也觉得犸莉安的观点太先进了

248
00:15:25,550 --> 00:15:28,720
I'm sorry. Who are you?
对不起，你是谁？

249
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:31,120
I'm a professor here. Ross Geller.
我是本校的教授罗斯盖勒

250
00:15:31,390 --> 00:15:35,060
Ross Geller? Why do I know that name? It's a...
罗斯盖勒？这个名字好熟 它是…

251
00:15:35,430 --> 00:15:36,450
Wait.
等一下

252
00:15:40,470 --> 00:15:41,760
Did you write this?
这本书是你写的吗？

253
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:44,130
Yes.
对

254
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:51,240
You're the person who checked out my book?
你就是借走我的书的人？

255
00:15:52,380 --> 00:15:56,940
You know,you look nothing like I would have thought.
你跟我想像中完全不一样

256
00:15:57,580 --> 00:15:59,070
You're so young.
你好年轻

257
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:04,050
Well, I skipped fourth grade.
我跳了四级

258
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:15,930
I am very,very sorry.
我真的很抱歉

259
00:16:24,950 --> 00:16:28,900
-So how was your date? -Great. We walked around the Village.
-你们的约会还顺利吗？ -太棒了，我们在格林威治村散步

260
00:16:29,150 --> 00:16:31,780
We went to this ice cream place. Split a milk shake.
还去了冰淇淋店，一起喝一杯奶昔

261
00:16:32,020 --> 00:16:33,680
Seventy-thirty, but still.
我喝的比较多，但那还是很棒

262
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:38,520
I'm thinking of taking her upstate to one of those bed and breakfasts.
我想带她到北区旅馆去过一夜

263
00:16:38,760 --> 00:16:41,020
Really? She said she wants to go?
真的吗？她答应了吗？

264
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:45,930
No, it's a surprise. It's gonna be tricky, because she's busy at work.
不，那是个惊喜，但那有点难 因为她的工作很忙

265
00:16:47,940 --> 00:16:51,270
Joey, look,honey, we need to talk,okay?
好吧，甜心，乔伊 我们得谈一谈，好吗？

266
00:16:53,670 --> 00:16:55,670
I got the feeling from her...
她让我觉得…

267
00:16:55,940 --> 00:17:00,350
that she's not looking for a serious relationship.
她不想认真地跟别人交往

268
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:04,040
-Where are you getting this? -She told me.
-你怎么会那么想？ -是她告诉我的

269
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:08,280
She said she's kind of a loner.
她说她是个独行侠

270
00:17:16,830 --> 00:17:19,130
-Joey.. -Hey, Rach, it's cool, you know.
-乔伊… -嘿，瑞秋，没关系的

271
00:17:19,330 --> 00:17:22,030
I'm a loner too, right?
我也是个独行侠，对吧？

272
00:17:23,170 --> 00:17:26,500
Hey, Joey. You know what? You are way too good for her.
乔伊，你知道吗？她配不上你

273
00:17:26,710 --> 00:17:31,640
I promise, next time I will tell them you're not looking for a relationship.
我发誓下次我会告诉她们 你不想定下来

274
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:37,480
No, don't do that. Just...
不，别那么做，只要…

275
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:42,480
-Next time, make sure she likes me. -Well, that too.
-下次确定她喜欢我 -对，你说的没错

276
00:17:47,660 --> 00:17:48,960
Joey?
乔伊？

277
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:54,360
-Do you want some pancakes? -Finally.
-你要吃煎饼吗？ -终于

278
00:17:58,370 --> 00:17:59,960
What are we gonna do?
我们该怎么办？

279
00:18:00,470 --> 00:18:02,200
I say we go with "Careless Whisper."
我们该选《无心呢喃》

280
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:07,370
Chandler?
钱德？

281
00:18:07,750 --> 00:18:10,220
Did she see us yet? Did she see us?
她看到我们了吗？

282
00:18:15,090 --> 00:18:17,080
Janice, what are you doing here?
珍妮丝，你来这里做什么？

283
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:20,120
I thought I was gonna go back to my apartment...
我想回我公寓去…

284
00:18:20,390 --> 00:18:25,420
but I just felt like I really couldn't be alone tonight.
但我觉得今晚我不想独处

285
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:34,870
I was just wondering if I could maybe stay here with you.
我在想或许我可以待在你们家

286
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:38,440
Just,I really feel like I need to be with family.
我真的觉得我该跟家人在一起

287
00:18:40,450 --> 00:18:43,580
Our kids are gonna call her Aunt Janice, aren't they?
我们的孩子会叫她 珍妮丝阿姨，对吧？

288
00:18:44,150 --> 00:18:49,090
Please. Because otherwise, I really don't know what I might do.
拜托，因为我真的不知道 我会做出什么事来

289
00:18:49,620 --> 00:18:53,390
Aren't you just a teensy bit curious?
你不会有点好奇吗？

290
00:18:54,390 --> 00:18:57,120
-You have any tissues? -Yeah, in the bathroom.
-你有面纸吗？ -有，在浴室里

291
00:19:00,970 --> 00:19:02,730
We'll just let her stay.
我们得收留她

292
00:19:02,940 --> 00:19:07,130
No. If we let her stay, she will stay forever.
不，如果我们收留她 她会永远住在这里

293
00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:11,610
-Kind of like your Barcalounger. -Is that what you're thinking about?
-就像你的巴卡兰吉 -你真的那么想？

294
00:19:11,810 --> 00:19:13,610
I never stop thinking about it.
我一直都是那么想

295
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:16,810
Hey, you guys?
你们还好吗？

296
00:19:17,050 --> 00:19:20,080
Do either one of you want to get in there before I take my bath?
你们想上洗手间吗？因为我要洗澡了

297
00:19:22,460 --> 00:19:24,290
Janice, I'm sorry...
珍妮丝，对不起…

298
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:27,860
but you can't stay here tonight.
但今晚你不能留下来

299
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:29,550
Why not?
为什么？

300
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:31,320
Honestly?
实情吗？

301
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:34,800
Our apartment is a hotbed...
我们家因为电磁辐射的关系…

302
00:19:35,070 --> 00:19:37,590
for electromagnetic activity.
遭到了污染

303
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:42,430
Monica and I have been immunized, but sadly...
摩妮卡跟我已经免疫了，但不幸地…

304
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:45,700
you have not.
你没有免疫力

305
00:19:51,990 --> 00:19:53,510
I'm gonna need a comforter.
我需要一条棉被

306
00:19:53,790 --> 00:19:57,280
Do you have a hypoallergenic one? Because otherwise I get very nasal.
你有抗过敏的棉被吗？ 不然的话我的鼻子会过敏

307
00:20:00,830 --> 00:20:04,290
Do you have a cat? Because it's already happening.
你们养了猫吗？ 因为我已经开始过敏了

308
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:06,360
Do you hear that? Listen.
你们听到了吗？你们听

309
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:13,000
Oh, my God! Oh, my God! You have to go.
我的天啊！你非离开不可

310
00:20:13,210 --> 00:20:14,200
Why?
为什么？

311
00:20:16,980 --> 00:20:19,540
Because Chandler still has feelings for you.
因为钱德对你还有感觉

312
00:20:23,150 --> 00:20:24,310
He does?
真的吗？

313
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:26,380
Say again?
你说什么？

314
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:29,420
That's right. That's right.
没错

315
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:32,720
And that is why you can't stay here tonight.
所以今晚你不能留下来

316
00:20:32,990 --> 00:20:36,120
And probably why you shouldn't come to the wedding.
或许你不该来参加婚礼

317
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:40,160
Feelings. Such strong feelings.
感觉，很强烈的感觉

318
00:20:41,570 --> 00:20:46,400
I mean,I realize that his feelings may never completely go away...
我是说我知道他对你的感觉 永远都不会完全消失…

319
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,670
but you can.
但你可以消失

320
00:20:49,780 --> 00:20:52,570
Oh, my God.
我的天啊

321
00:20:52,850 --> 00:20:56,440
I understand. I am so sorry.
我了解，我真的很抱歉

322
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:58,080
I'll go.
我会离开的

323
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:04,950
Goodbye, Monica.
再见，摩妮卡

324
00:21:05,230 --> 00:21:09,250
I wish you a lifetime of happiness with him.
我祝你跟他永远幸福快乐

325
00:21:09,460 --> 00:21:10,520
Chandler.
钱德

326
00:21:12,530 --> 00:21:14,800
You call me when this goes in the pooper.
如果你们处得不好 你可以打电话给我

327
00:21:27,850 --> 00:21:29,750
I've got this section covered.
这区由我负责

328
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:32,950
Yeah,in fact,I've got this baby to shine in people's eyes.
事实上我会拿着手电筒 照别人的眼睛…

329
00:21:33,220 --> 00:21:34,920
Okay, see you later.
好吧，待会见

330
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:47,560
I just wanted to show Monica your book.
我只是带摩妮卡来看你的书

331
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000


332
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
